    {
      "key": "chartRenderWorkspaceDirectoryHint",
      "en": "Temporary files are written here while rendering. Leave the default unless the drive is too small.",
      "zh": "渲染时临时视频和音频会写在这里。除非磁盘空间不够，否则保持默认即可。"
    },
    {
